OL,5,G1600 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FThe interceptors pursue of a
OL,7,     Froadworks wrecker, a 17-year-old
OL,8,     Frobbery suspect, and a drink
OL,9,     Fdriver who doesn't understand the
OL,10,     Fword 'blow'.
OL,11,G1700 Call the Bailiffs: Time to Pay Up!
OL,12,     FIn London, Scott and police
OL,13,     Fofficers remove squatters from a
OL,14,     Fcouncil-owned building where
OL,15,     Fthey've been living for nearly a
OL,16,     Fyear. But one woman barricades
OL,17,     Fherself in a room.
OL,18,G1800 Home and Away
OL,19,     FRichie gets another shot. Jo digs
OL,20,     Fherself a deeper hole with Tane.
OL,21,     FTane's called to visit his family.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
