OL,5,G1830 Home and Away
OL,6,     FA life hangs in the balance. Cash
OL,7,     Freceives shocking news. There's a
OL,8,     Fnew doctor in the Bay.
OL,9,G1900 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,10,     FA woman suffers with chronic back
OL,11,     Fpain since giving birth to her
OL,12,     Ftwins five years ago. During the
OL,13,     Fprocedure, Hannah was given an
OL,14,     Fepidural that caused nerve damage
OL,15,     Fin her spine.
OL,16,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,17,     FThe staff and patients of
OL,18,     FBarnsley's A&E department are put
OL,19,     Funder the microscope. 84-year-old
OL,20,     FTerry, comes in with a
OL,21,     Fbadly-broken ankle and fears he
OL,22,     Fmay never dance again.
